"<div>\n<i class=\"NoteType\">\nPerson Note\n</i>\n<div class=\"grampsstylednote\">\n<p>\nA short version of this confusing mess, as best as I understand it:\n</p>\n<p>\n1853: Ellen Hanson marries Henry Scott<br />\n1858: Ellen's sister Hannah marries Edwin Broadley.<br />\nabout 1860: Edwin dies, and Hannah marries again to John Puddicombe.<br />\n1881: Henry dies, leaving Ellen widowed.<br />\n1891: Hannah dies, leaving John widowed and just making it into the 1891 census.<br />\n1892: John and Ellen end up marrying each other\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
